(172, 1392761598, '品牌市场推广专员', 'HEINEKEN USA', 'Resturant', '', 'United States', 'New York', 'New York', 0.000000, 0.000000, 'United States', 'New York', 'New York', 'None', 'Full Time', '<div class="description-section">\n<div class="rich-text">\n<p><strong>HEINEKEN BRAND ACTIVATOR &ndash; MULTICULTURAL MARKETS &ndash; METRO NYC</strong></p>\n<p>*An Asian (Chinese or Korean segments) focus in Metro NY</p>\n<p>&nbsp;Job Type:Full-time, calendar year 2014 &lsquo;at-will&rsquo; contract position with Agency</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;Position Summary:</p>\n<p>The Heineken Brand Activator serves as a dedicated resource serving the Multicultural segment in the assigned territory with a thorough understanding of the industry, key competitors, market position, distribution channels and legal parameters. The Heineken Brand Activator is held accountable for the planning and execution of local and brand marketing programs at retailers in the assigned territory.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;Key Responsibilities:</p>\n<p>&bull;Partner with the Heineken Urban Market Managers and Heineken Commercial Marketing to develop a plan for the assigned territory and focus market (Hispanic, Asian or African-American)</p>\n<p>&bull;Execute plan within the assigned territory and focus market</p>\n<p>&bull;Activate local and brand marketing programs at retail</p>\n<p>&bull;Assist with promotional set up of both on- and off-premise activities</p>\n<p>&bull;Work within Heineken standards</p>\n<p>&bull;Identify and act upon improvement opportunities</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;Key Objectives:</p>\n<p>1.Create brand awareness among brand&rsquo;s target market</p>\n<p>2.Educate consumers about key brand attributes</p>\n<p>3.Increase consumer trial</p>\n<p>4.Create a positive association between promotional experience and brand</p>\n<p>5.Establish and enhance the relationship with retailers, wholesaler and bar/wait staff</p>\n<p>6.Increase Rate of Sale</p>\n<p>7.Support New Distribution</p>\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Qualifications:</p>\n<p>&bull;Bachelor&rsquo;s degree plus 1-2 years of Sales or Marketing experience</p>\n<p>&bull;CPG or Beverage experience</p>\n<p>&bull;Bilingual, as needed (Spanish for Hispanic focus position / Mandarin, Cantonese or Korean for Asian focus position)</p>\n<p>&bull;Must have a vehicle</p>\n<p>&bull;It is preferred but not required to have knowledge in the beer market/ bar + restaurant industry/ different retail accounts ( grocery stores, supermarkets, chain stores, etc.)</p>\n<p>&bull;Please also submit a cover letter stating for which market you will be suitable ( Hispanic, Asian, African-American)</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;Key Competencies: &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&bull;Be Brave</p>\n<p>&bull;Decide &amp; Do</p>\n<p>&bull;Hunt as a Pack</p>\n<p>&bull;Take it Personally</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;Physical Demands:</p>\n<p>While performing the duties of this job, the employee is regularly required to use hands to finger, handle, or feel; reach with hands and arms; and talk or hear. &nbsp;The employee frequently is required to walk and sit. &nbsp;The demands described here are representative of those that must be met by an employee to successfully perform the essential functions of this job.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Work Environment:</p>\n<p>The work environment characteristics described here are representative of those an employee encounters while performing the essential functions of this job. While performing the duties of this job, the employee is occasionally exposed to moving mechanical parts and outside weather conditions. &nbsp;The noise level in the work environment is usually moderate.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="skills-section">\n<h3 class="sub-header">Desired Skills and Experience</h3>\n<div class="rich-text">\n<p>Salary:&nbsp;USD 30000 - 35000 Per Year</p>\n<p>Experience Required:&nbsp;1+ to 2 Years</p>\n<p>Education Required:&nbsp;Bachelor''s Degree</p>\n</div>\n</div>', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs2/view/10789316?trk=vsrp_jobs_res_name&trkInfo=VSRPsearchId:568703801392760915923,VSRPtargetId:10789316,VSRPcmpt:primary', '', 45, 189, 2),
