(169, 1392707611, '管理培训生项目', '高级人才招聘与人才管理公司Hudson (翰德中国) ', 'Management', 'Beijing, China', 'China', 'Beijing', 'Beijing', 39.904030, 116.407524, '中国', '北京市', '北京', 'None', 'Full Time', '<p>享誉全球的高级人才招聘与人才管理公司Hudson (翰德中国) 管理培训生项目开始招募了！为期25周的培训将让你变成一流的职业规划师！</p>\n<h4>Fast Track Promotion!; Fun &amp; Dynamic Working Environment; Annual Package Plus Quarterly Bonus Scheme</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>&nbsp;Fast track your career</li>\n<li>&nbsp;World class training, by experienced professionals</li>\n<li>&nbsp;Fun, dynmic, challenging, rewarding</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Hudson is a global talent solutions company with a strong presence in the Asia Pacific region. We are growing our business in Asia and hence are recruiting Associate Consultants within our Management Trainee Program in Hong Kong.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Our 25 week program provides you with step by step world class theory and on the job training on how to be a successful recruitment consultant.&nbsp;&nbsp;In line with our philosophy of transparency and meritocracy, how soon you are promoted to a Consultant role will depend solely on your performance on this program.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li>&nbsp;Do you want to start your career with a leading multinational company?</li>\n<li>&nbsp;Do you want to be trained on how to be a world class recruitment consultant?</li>\n<li>&nbsp;Do you want to get promoted based on merit and not on years of experience?</li>\n<li>&nbsp;Do you want to build and lead a team in the near future?</li>\n<li>&nbsp;Do you want to work in an environment that pushes you to achieve your potential and recognises you for your achievements?</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>If your answer is&nbsp;<strong>&ldquo;Yes&rdquo;,&nbsp;</strong>then<strong>&nbsp;</strong>we at Hudson are interested in talking with you. We are looking for highly motivated graduates with up to 2 years experience and a track record of excellence who want to be the best and have the drive, energy and commitment to succeed in this rewarding