ont-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: disc;">Plan, coordinate and execute a wide variety of meetings, office and client luncheons, dinners, client visits and notify attendees</li>\n<li style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 17px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: disc;">Manage office meetings and conference room schedules and setup including beverage/food order</li>\n<li style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 17px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: disc;">Assist in planning, executing and attending company outings and events</li>\n<li style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 17px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: disc;">Make travel arrangements as requested for managers and staff, including follow up and communication of any flight, hotel, or other related itinerary changes to traveler&nbsp;</li>\n<li style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 17px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: disc;">Organize the cleaning of conference rooms, kitchen and refrigerator as needed</li>\n<li style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 17px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: disc;">Assist and participate in annual Catapult Kids Day event</li>\n</ul>\n<p style="margin: