ace">&nbsp;</span><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" /><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" />Expand CIWA program and projects<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" />&bull; Establish and work with contacts at UW-Tacoma and UW-Bothell on development of projects<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" />&bull; Contact other state-supported institutions of higher education in the State of Washington to identify and develop appropriate CIWA projects<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" /><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" />Outreach, Advancement, and Communications<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" />&bull; Coordinate CIWA activities with the Alliance for Education, Seattle Public Schools, and the Office of the Superintendent of Public Instruction and jointly work with interested K-12 school systems across the State of Washington<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" />&bull; Act as CIWA representative on committees, including the Education Advisory Board &bull; Develop on-going relationships with potential donors and corporate partners, in cooperation with UW/OGA Advancement Office<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" />&bull; Develop joint community outreach activities with the Department of Asian Languages and Literature and the Jackson School of International Studies East Asia Center<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" /><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" />General Administration<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" />&bull; Maintain program email and phone/voicemail, and compile and maintain email distribution lists<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" />&bull; Maintain website, including updating content</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n<td class="TDRegular" style="margin: 0px; padding: 10px 4px 4px; border: 0px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: middle; text-align: left; float: none !important; color: black;" colspan="3" align="left" width="10%">REQUIREMENTS:</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n<td class="TDRegular" style="margin: 0px; padding: 4px; border: 0px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: normal; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: middle; text-align: left; float: none !important; color: black; background-color: #ffffff; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;" colspan="3">&bull; A Master''s degree in China Studies, International Studies, or a related field, and two years'' relevant work experience.<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" />&bull; Excellent written and verbal communication skills.<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" />&bull; <strong>Fluency in speaking and reading Chinese (Mandarin and/or Cantonese preferred).&nbsp;<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span></strong><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" />\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 1.3em; vertical-align: baseline;"><em style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">Equivalent education/experience will substitute for all minimum qualifications except when there are legal requirements, such as a license/certification/registration.</em></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n<td class="TDRegular" style="margin: 0px; padding: 10px 4px 4px; border: 0px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: middle; text-align: left; float: none !important; color: black;" colspan="3" align="left" width="10%">DESIRED:</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n<td class="TDRegular" style="margin: 0px; padding: 4px; border: 0px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: normal; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: middle; text-align: left; float: none !important; color: black; background-color: #ffffff; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;" colspan="3">Experience with:<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" />&bull; Grant writing and grant management<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" />&bull; Fundraising and donor stewardship<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" />&