(366, 1397883632, 'Modeler needed for a bank', 'Major Bank at Buffalo', 'Finance', 'Buffalo, NY, United States', 'United States', 'New York', 'Buffalo', 42.886448, -78.878372, '美国', '纽约州', '布法罗', 'None', 'Full Time', '<p>THIS IS A RARE&nbsp;OPPORTUNITY FOR FRESH STATISTICS GRADUATE TO GET INTO BANKING BUSINESS AS A MODELER.</p>\n<p>PREFER STATISTICS MASTER OR HIGHER, FRESH GRADUATE WELLCOME, BUT sas SKILLS HAS TO BE SUFFICIENT AND MUST BE A QUICK LEARNER BOTH IN PEOPLE SKILL AND TECHNICAL SKILLS.</p>\n<p>MORE THAN ONE POSITION, TECHNICAL HELP FROM A EXPERIENCE MODELR AVAILABLE FOR THESE SPECIFIC POSITIONS.</p>\n<p>NEED TO BE IMMEDIATELY AVAILABLE. ONE YEAR COMMITMENT GUARANTEED, IF PERFORMANCE IS GOOD, LONG TERM POSSIBLE (MAY BE PROVIDED OPPORTUNITY TO JOIN A START-UP COMPANY (BASED IN SOUTHERN CALIFORNIA, SPECIALIZED IN BANKING SOFTWARE) IF QUALIFIED). $35-45/H. H1B VISA POSSIBLE, BUT NOT QUARANTEED.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '', 'garfield_200200@yahoo.com', 524, 103, 2),
(369, 1398096164, '中文助理', 'Baker Tilly', 'Finance', 'Chicago, IL, United States', 'United States', 'Illinois', 'Chicago', 41.878113, -87.629799, '美国', '伊利诺伊州', '芝加哥', 'None', 'Full Time', '<h2 class="medium" style="margin: 1.5em 0px 1em; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.2em; font-weight: bold; text-transform: uppercase; color: #333333; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">DESCRIPTION</h2>\n<div class="content" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333333; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">Baker Tilly Virchow Krause&rsquo;s values of integrity, passion and stewardship define us as an organization and an employer. We recognize that our approach, strategy and culture are driven by our people. Their focus and commitment has resulted in Baker Tilly Virchow Krause being ranked as one of the top 20 largest public accounting and advisory firms in the United States and our offices consistently earning &ldquo;best place to work&rdquo; honors. Our people have been fundamental in getting us to where we are today and where we will go in the future.&nbsp;We are seeking an<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">International Assistant</strong><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>to work closely with executives from Baker Tilly affiliates from other nations providing support as they acclimate to various differences in language, the country&rsquo;s culture and Baker Tilly Virchow Krause&rsquo;s culture.&nbsp;<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">It&rsquo;s an exciting time to join Baker Tilly!</strong>&nbsp;Baker Tilly Virchow Krause is ranked as one of the top 20 largest public accounting and advisory firms in the United States. With a staff of more than 1600, Baker Tilly provides a wide range of accounting, tax, assurance and consulting services to premier companies and leading organizations in industries that drive our economy. As an independent member of Baker Tilly International, the world&rsquo;s 8th largest network of accounting firms (with a combined worldwide revenue of $3 billion) we bring our clients and our people access to market-specific knowledge in more than 125 countries.ResponsibilitiesProvide cultural guidance.\n<ul style="margin: 5px 0px 5px 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; list-style: disc;">\n<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; list-style: disc;">Advise, as needed, on appropriate use of the English language.</li>\n<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; list-style: disc;">Advise, as needed, on appropriate cultural customs and behaviors.</li>\n<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; list-style: disc;">Assist in traveling and locating points of interest.</li>\n<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; list-style: disc;">Provides other advice relating to conducting business and living in the United States.&nbsp;</li>\n</ul>\nProvide high level administrative support to visiting executive.\n<ul style="margin: 5px 0px 5px 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; list-style: disc;">\n<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; list-style: disc;">Contact and respond to high ranking individuals.</li>\n<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; list-style: disc;">Makes decisions on the behalf of the executive as delegated.</li>\n<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; list-style: disc;">Ensure requests for action or information are relayed to the appropriate person for response.</li>\n<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; list-style: disc;">Composes correspondence from minimal or no notation.&nbsp; Handles sensitive and confidential information on a regular basis with discretion.\n<ul style="margin: 5px 0px 5px 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; list-style: disc;">\n<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; list-style: disc;">Correspondence may be in English or in executive&rsquo;s home language.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; list-style: disc;">Handles sensitive and confidential information on a regular basis with discretion</li>\n<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; list-style: disc;">Screen executive&rsquo;s telephone calls.&nbsp;</li>\n<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; list-style: disc;">Assist with management and special projects.</li>\n<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; list-style: disc;">Maintains the executive&rsquo;s calendar and travel logistics.<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</strong></li>\n</ul>\nAssist with general office functions.\n<ul style="margin: 5px 0px 5px 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; list-style: disc;">\n<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; list-style: disc;">Opens and distributes mail, schedules and prepares materials for meetings, coordinates collection and preparation of operating reports, such as budget expenditures, and statistical records of performance data.</li>\n<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; list-style: disc;">Maintain paper-based and electronic files.</li>\n<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; list-style: disc;">Assists on projects as needed.<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</strong></li>\n</ul>\nMaintain and expand knowledge base in area of expertise.\n<ul style="margin: 5px 0px 5px 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; list-style: disc;">\n<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; list-style: disc;">Attend courses to develop and keep skills and knowledge current.</li>\n<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; list-style: disc;">Comply with continuing education requirements.</li>\n<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; list-style: disc;">Increase efficiencies, technical ability and interpersonal skills.<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</strong></li>\n</ul>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -- Other duties as assigned.</div>\n<h2 class="medium" style="margin: 1.5em 0px 1em; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.2em; font-weight: bold; text-transform: uppercase; color: #333333; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">REQUIREMENTS</h2>\n<div class="content" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333333; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">\n<ul style="margin: 5px 0px 5px 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; list-style: 