 parents by engaging and caring for the children in daily activities and pleasantly greeting and communicating with parents on a daily basis</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span style="font-size: 12px;"><br /><strong>Qualifications</strong></span><span style="font-size: 12px;"><br /></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style="font-size: 12px;">Fluency in English as well Spanish, Manadarin or Sign Language</span></li>\n<li><span style="font-size: 12px;">Bachelors degee in TESOL preferred<br /></span></li>\n<li><span style="font-size: 12px;">Experience in teaching second languages to children ages 3-6 years</span></li>\n<li><span style="font-size: 12px;">At least nine credits in early childhood preferred<br /></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span style="font-size: 12px;">We offer competitive salaries and benefit packages.​</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'http://jobview.monster.com/Mandarin-Early-Childhood-Teacher-Job-Chicago-IL-US-133163242.aspx', '', 5, 163, 2),
