ach programs<br />&bull;&nbsp;Explain customer/member specific plan of benefits&nbsp;<br />&bull;&nbsp;Consistent and accurate data&nbsp; entry</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div>Skills:<br />&bull;&nbsp;Fluent in Chinese<br />&bull;&nbsp;Knowledge of Managed Long Term Care is helpful<br />&bull;&nbsp;Insurance background helpful&nbsp;<br />&bull;&nbsp;Data entry skills with an 98% accuracy and 60wpm keying aptitude</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div><br />Additional Details:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />&bull;&nbsp;Pay Rate: $10.50 per hour<br />&bull;&nbsp;Hours: Full Time positions available<br />&bull;&nbsp;Employment Type: long-term contract&nbsp;<br />&bull;&nbsp;Limited medical and dental coverage for contractors and their families available immediately<br />&bull;&nbsp;Opportunities for professional growth.</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div><br />Integrity Staffing Solutions is an Equal Opportunity Employer. All job offers are contingent upon the successful completion of a background check and drug screen.</div>', 'http://jobs.integritystaffing.com/job/New-York-Bi-Lingual-CSR-Job-NY/32415100/?feedId=604&utm_source=Indeed&utm_medium=organic&utm_campaign=Indeed', '', 5, 106, 2),
