(617, 1407776403, '销售 经理', 'E-CARGOWAY EXPRESS', 'Marketing', 'Compton, CA, United States', 'United States', 'California', 'Compton', 33.895847, -118.220070, '美利坚合众国', '加利福尼亚州', '康普顿', 'None', 'Full Time', '<p><strong>职位标签</strong><strong>:</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;渠道销售 sales manager</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>职位职能</strong><strong>:</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;业务拓展主管/经理,大客户管理 Sales Business Development &nbsp;Manager</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>职位描述</strong><strong>:</strong></p>\n<p>岗位描述</p>\n<p>Job Summary<br /> <br /> 1. 管理易网国际速递的市场销售团队，<br /> 2. 制定并领导完成易网国际速递的销售预算与计划，<br /> 3. 设计并持续完善易网国际速递的产品与服务。</p>\n<p>4. 工作内容主要为销售出口至中国的个人快件物品。</p>\n<p>1. The management of E-Cargoway express delivery marketing sales team,<br /> 2. Develop and lead the complete website, international express delivery of sales budget and plan,<br /> 3. Design and continuously improve the website, international express delivery of products and services.<br /> 4. The work content mainly exports to China for the sale of personal express items.<br /> <br /> 工作职责</p>\n<p>Job responsibilities<br /> <br /> 1. 制定公司销售预算与计划，并领导团队完成销售计划，持续为客户提供优质的服务，提高客户满意度，<br /> 2. 发掘销售机会，拓展大客户销售 <br /> 3. 分析客户需求与行业发展，通过团队协助，设计并发展相应的解决方案，并持续完善成为公司服务产品，<br /> 4. 统计与管理日常销售数据与报表，持续优化团队的工作绩效<br /> 1. Make company sales budget and plan, and lead the team to complete the sales plan, and continue to provide customers with quality service, improve customer satisfaction,<br /> 2. Develop sales opportunities, expand key account sales<br /> 3. Analyze customer requirements and industry development, through the team work, design and development of the corresponding solutions, and continuously improve the company services products,<br /> 4. Daily sales data and report statistics and management, continuously optimize the performance of team work</p>\n<p><br /> 任职要求</p>\n<p>Job specification<br /> <br /> 1. 3-5年的销售经验，具有一定国际物流，电子商务市场开发，国际快件，仓储服务等销售经验为佳，<br /> 2. 优先考虑具有B2C电子商务网站，亚马逊等推广及转运物流销售产品或服务的工作经验，<br /> 3. 2-3年的销售团队管理经验，<br /> 4. 工作以结果为导向，热情主动且富有激情，<br /> 5. 很强的内外部沟通能力，团队合作能力，逻辑思考能力与执行力，<br /> 6. 为人真诚，工作有责任心，具有一定的创业精神</p>\n<p>7. 美籍华人或者精通中文的优先</p>\n<p>8. 需要持有美国绿卡或者长期居住证</p>\n<p>1. 3-5 years of sales experience, has certain international logistics, e-commerce market development, international express, warehousing services such as sales experience is preferred,<br /> 2. Preferred B2C e-commerce sites, such as amazon and transport logistics working experience in sales of products or services,<br /> 3. 2-3 years experience in managing a sales team,<br /> 4. Work results oriented, enthusiasm and passion,<br /> 5. Strong internal and external communication skills and team cooperation ability, logical thinking ability and executive ability,<br /> 6. Sincere, has the sense of responsibility to the work, have a certain entrepreneurial spirit<br /> 7. A Chinese-American or proficient in Chinese is preferred<br /> 8. Need to hold US green card or long-term residence permit</p>', '', 'lax-john@ecargoway.com', 1020, 119, 2),
