(746, 1413693207, 'SALES & MARKETING COORDINATOR销售&市场协调员', 'Dai Cheong Trading Company, Inc', 'Marketing', 'Los Angeles, CA, United States', 'United States', 'California', 'Los Angeles', 34.052235, -118.243683, '美利坚合众国', '加利福尼亚州', '洛杉矶', 'None', 'Full Time', '<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class="snip">\n<p>BI-LINGUAL SALES &amp; MARKETING COORDINATOR (English + Chinese/Vietnamese)</p>\n<p>Company: Dai Cheong Trading Inc.<br />Industry: Food Importing &amp; Distribution<br />Location: Los Angeles, CA (warehouse district) 90031<br />Career Level: Entry Level Sales &amp; Marketing</p>\n<p>Dai Cheong Trading Inc. is rapidly expanding its distribution nationwide. We are seeking a bi-lingual coordinator help grow the business. This person must be comfortable working in both Chinese and in English (ideally also in Vietnamese -the more Asian languages, the better!).</p>\n<p>ROLES &amp; RESPONSIBILITIES:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Receive and process orders</li>\n<li>Manage and grow existing accounts (retail stores and online)</li>\n<li>Coordinator with overseas suppliers</li>\n<li>Coordinate and attend trade shows and street fairs</li>\n<li>Create sales and progress reports</li>\n<li>Forecast inventory</li>\n<li>Respond to email inquiries</li>\n<li>Other administrative projects as needed</li>\n</ul>\n<p>QUALIFICATIONS:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Education: College level graduate</li>\n<li>Languages: MUST be at least bi-lingual (English, Cantonese, Mandarin, Vietnamese)</li>\n<li>Computer: Proficient in Microsoft Word, Excel, Powerpoint., and Photoshop</li>\n<li>Communication: Excellent verbal and written/email communication required.</li>\n<li>Must be comfortable working in an Asian culture environment.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>BENEFITS:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Competitive Base Salary (Entry Level DOE)</li>\n<li>Health &amp; Medical Benefits</li>\n<li>Paid vacation, holidays and sick days</li>\n<li>Casual Family Culture</li>\n</ul>\n<p>ABOUT THE COMPANY:<br />Asian (Ethnic) 