rg&nbsp;</p>', 'http://www.youmayus.org/', 'joecy@youmayus.org', 1341, 242, 2),
(775, 1414620214, '销售助理', 'Import / Export', 'Marketing', 'San Jose, CA, United States', 'United States', 'California', 'San Jose', 37.339386, -121.894958, '美国', '加利福尼亚州', '圣何塞', 'None', 'Full Time', '<p>An Import/Export company in San Jose is looking for a responsible individual for a full-time position.</p>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Computer Savvy</li>\n<li>Good command of English</li>\n<li>Detail orientated</li>\n<li>Strong analytical skill</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Qualified candidates please apply with resum&eacute; and expected salarly. We can petition H-1 for you if you can prove to us that you are capable and responsible.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '', '', 1342, 144, 2),
