(786, 1415143774, '中文接待员', 'Proactive', 'Language', 'New York, NY, United States', 'United States', 'New York', 'New York', 40.712784, -74.005943, '美国', '纽约', '纽约', 'None', 'Full Time', '<p>Mandarin Cantonese and English Speaking Receptionist needed for a busy Pediatric Occupational and Physical Therapy gym located in Brooklyn. A friendly receptionist is needed to answer phones, coordinate schedules and visits, and take care of paperwork and filing. Prior experience working in an office a definite plus.</p>\n<p>Candidates must be individuals who are detail oriented, with the ability to multi-task and stay organized.</p>\n<p>Knowledge of Word, Excel, PowerPoint and general computer skills a must.</p>\n<p>Good presentation, people skills and communication skills are a necessity.</p>\n<p>Part or Full Time Position available. Flexible hours between (Sundays 9:00 to 5:00, Mon to Thu 2:30 to 8:30 and Friday 10:00 to 6:00)</p>', 'http://www.indeed.com/cmp/Proactive/jobs/Bilingual-Chinese-Receptionist-bf938f7469debebc', '', 980, 219, 2),
(787, 1415143897, '营销部经理', 'NHC Health Management Corporation', 'Marketing', 'Los Angeles, CA, United States', 'United States', 'California', 'Los Angeles', 34.052235, -118.243683, '美国', '加利福尼亚州', '洛杉矶', 'None', 'Full Time', '<p>Duties:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Implements marketing and advertising campaigns by assembling and analyzing sales forecasts; preparing marketing and advertising strategies, plans, and objectives; planning and organizing promotional presentations; updating calendars.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Tracks sales and costs by analyzing and entering sales, expense, and new business data.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Prepares marketing reports by collecting, analyzing, and summarizing sales data.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Keeps promotional materials ready by coordinating requirements with graphics department; inventorying stock; placing orders; verifying receipt.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Supports sales staff by providing sales data, market trends, forecasts, account analyses, new product information; relaying customer services requests.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Researches competitive products by identifying and evaluating project characteristics, market share, pricing, and advertising; maintaining research databases.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Plans meetings and trade shows by identifying, assembling, and coordinating requirements; establishing contacts; developing schedules and assignments; coordinating mailing lists.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Monitors budgets by comparing and analyzing actual results with plans and forecasts.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Updates job knowledge by participating in educational opportunities; reading trade publications.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Accomplishes organization goals by accepting ownership for accomplishing new and different requests; exploring opportunities to add value to job accomplishments.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Skills/Qualifications:<br />Direct Marketing, Market Segmentation, Marketing Research, Coordination, Project Management, Reporting Research Resu