sults &bull; Good critical thinking and persuasive communication skills &bull; Previous cold-calling/face-to-face sales experience is a PLUS &bull; Previous experience in the Merchant Service industry is a PLUS &bull; Bilingual skills in Spanish, Korean, Chinese and English are a PLUS Compensations: &bull; Base payment with minimum quota requirement &bull; Commission per complete account and monthly achievement bonus &bull; Residual income (accumulated recurring income) &bull; Promotion opportunities based on quarterly performance review Notes: This is NOT an investment banking or financial markets position. We provide payment solutions and merchant services to business owners mainly in retail sector. We can provide H1B visa for the year of 2014-2015. Contact: Email:susanz@uprocessing.com Phone:646 455 9439</p>', 'http://www.uprocessing.com/en/', 'susanz@uprocessing.com', 1376, 195, 2),
(805, 1415609317, ' 急招中文辅导老师 急急急', '家教', 'Language', '美国纽约州纽约', 'United States', 'New York', 'New York', 40.712784, -74.005943, '美国', '纽约', '纽约', 'None', 'Part Time', '<p><em></em></p>\n<p>职位技能要求： 工作时间：每周一到周五，或者每周做2-3天，具体时间由您自己决定！<br /> 每天10点到下午1点左右。<br />工作内容：负责3个班级的中文课程，每个班级10-15人。每天上午10点开始上课，每个班的课大概是30分钟-1个小时，时间由您自己把握！只要是中国人就能教！讲讲话就可以了，还可以穿</p>\n<p>插放电影，教室有投影仪，黑板等！<br />工作对象：黑人小学生，都是有钱人的孩子，根据年龄分成3个班；5-7岁一个班；7-10岁一个班；10-12岁一个班；学生都是0基础，很好教。</p>\n<p>背景：是一个学校搞的夏令营，学生们早上9点前被送到学校，一天要上很多课程，包括音乐，舞蹈，钢琴，足球，美术，等等，所以中文只是其中之一而已。下午3点钟，每个孩子就被司机<br />接回家了。<br />标签：高薪招聘中文英文辅导老师<br />有意者发简历至luhaiqingkaixing@gmail.com验证</p>', '', 'luhaiqingkaixing@gmail.com', 1381, 5, 2),
