(813, 1415975446, '采购专员 - Entry Level （主要负责跟中国供应商联系下订单）', 'Powder City LLC', 'International Commerce', 'York, PA, United States', 'United States', 'Pennsylvania', 'York', 39.962597, -76.727745, '美利坚合众国', 'Pennsylvania', 'York', 'H1B', 'Part Time', '<p>DOE</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Powder City is seeking an entry-level sourcing specialist. Candidates must be able to speak fluent Mandarin and conversant English. The ability to read and write in both English and Simplified Chinese is also required.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>This is a part-time position at 20-30 hours weekly, depending on your availability. An eventual full-time position is possible for the right candidate.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>RESPONSIBILITIES</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>* Sourcing and obtaining quotes for raw materials</p>\n<p>* Negotiating prices between suppliers</p>\n<p>* Assisting with ordering and watching inventory levels for reorder points</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>REQUIREMENTS</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>* Fluent in Mandarin</p>\n<p>* Able to read and write Simplified Chinese</p>\n<p>* Conversant in English</p>\n<p>* Able to read and write in English</p>\n<p>* Basic spreadsheet knowledge</p>\n<p>* Basic statistical knowledge preferred</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>HOURS</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>* 20-30 hours weekly to start</p>\n<p>* Full-time is available for those able to take on additional responsibilities</p>\n<p>* 9am-4pm three to four weekdays</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>TO APPLY</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Please send your resume along with answers to the questions below:</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>* Do you have any existing purchasing or sourcing experience?</p>\n<p lang="zxx">* How do you change a relative cell reference to an absolute cell reference in a spreadsheet?</p>\n<p lang="zxx">* Do you have any knowledge in basic statistics?</p>\n<p lang="zxx">&nbsp;</p>\n<p lang="zxx">我是代为招人的，Powder City是一家刚起步的卖保健品营养粉的美国公司，因为货源很多是来自中国，所以他们需要找一位英语中文都能进行交流的采购人员。一开始是part-time，每周大概只会工作20-30小时，如果表现好可以转为全职。每天的工作全部在电脑上完成，发发邮件下下订单，在公司系统里面做做简单的数据分析，必须会使用excel。英语中文必须沟通无障碍。</p>\n<p lang="zxx">&nbsp;</p>\n<p lang="zxx">公司没什么福利，没有保险，只有paid time off，由具体的工作时间而定。关于H1B sponsor我没有具体问过老板，但是既然他们要找一个会说中文的，应该有可能会愿意给sponsor，只不过钱可能需要你自己出。</p>\n<p lang="zxx">申请职位请看以下链接:</p>\n<p lang="zxx">http://www.powdercity.com/pages/jr-sourcing-specialist</p>\n<p lang="zxx">http://www.indeed.com/viewjob?jk=a36e1b32b0292146&amp;q=sourcing&amp;l=York,+PA&amp;tk=1979t481t0nl12v1&amp;from=web&amp;advn=4429138125964578&amp;sjdu=u-yoggoEhSaEaGJItG6F_uBc3Uvfw01xj1c6hn-b7_tlmnMPGhBUdPjLF_GyMRqfGyAb9fQ7r0ENCSnNPBRK-g&amp;pub=pub-indeed</p>\n<p lang="zxx">&nbsp;</p>\n<p lang="zxx">&nbsp;</p>', 'http://www.powdercity.com/pages/jr-sourcing-specialist', 'letacrystal@126.com', 1389, 304, 2),
(814, 1416074399, '电子商务公司全职运维经理和系统操作收货退货服务', 'SmartMoney LLC', 'Marketing', 'Fremont, CA, United States', 'United States', 'California', 'Fremont', 37.548271, -121.988571, '美国', '加利福尼亚州', '弗里蒙特', 'H1B', 'Full Time', '<p>地处Fremont automall parkway 和fremont blvd。业务扩展<br />退单跟踪，报价订单管理，仓库业务维护等，卖家，卖家ebay 沟通等<br />底薪2500美元，绩效奖金500美元以上<br />诚招能长期稳定，认真细心负责的业务人士加盟。如果你富有开拓精神，有广阔的发展空间，能提升能力和收入</p>', '', 'lubinwang@yahoo.com', 1391, 149, 2),
