(817, 1416334552, '急聘全职办公室助理一名', 'DCS', 'Marketing', 'New York, NY, United States', 'United States', 'New York', 'New York', 40.712784, -74.005943, '美国', '纽约', '纽约', 'None', 'Full Time', '<p class="p16">因业务发展需要，本公司现对外招聘办公室助理一名，招聘要求如下：</p>\n<p class="p16"><!-- [if !supportLists]-->1．&nbsp;<!--[endif]-->年龄20-35岁；</p>\n<p class="p16"><!-- [if !supportLists]-->2．&nbsp;<!--[endif]-->工作细心认真，诚实有责任心，吃苦耐劳。</p>\n<p class="p16"><!-- [if !supportLists]-->3．&nbsp;<!--[endif]-->有一定业务经验，聪明反应快，工作有条理。</p>\n<p class="p16"><!-- [if !supportLists]-->4．&nbsp;<!--[endif]-->熟悉基础电脑操作，如Excel等office软件；</p>\n<p class="p16"><!-- [if !supportLists]-->5．&nbsp;<!--[endif]-->有基本的中英文沟通能力；</p>\n<p class="p16"><!-- [if !supportLists]-->6．&nbsp;<!--[endif]-->会基本的账目计算，懂得使用金蝶财务软件优先录用；</p>\n<p class="p16"><!-- [if !supportLists]-->7．&nbsp;<!--[endif]-->有客服基本素质：待人有礼，语气温和，能忍耐无理吵闹等。</p>\n<p class="p16">有意者请致电：(917)539-8900</p>\n<p class="p16">或将简历发送至：dcssandy@gmail.com</p>\n<p class="p16">联系人：Sandy</p>\n<p class="p16">公司地址：6809&nbsp;FORT&nbsp;HAMILTON&nbsp;PKWY</p>\n<p class="p16">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;BROOKLYN,&nbsp;NY&nbsp;11219(好运来超市斜对面)</p>', '', 'dcssandy@gmail.com', 1405, 0, 2),
(818, 1416367209, '市场调查员', 'MIKADO Marketing', 'Marketing', 'Los Angeles, CA, United States', 'United States', 'California', 'Los Angeles', 34.052235, -118.243683, '美国', '加利福尼亚州', '洛杉矶', 'None', 'Full Time', '<div id="job_header"><strong class="jobtitle"><span style="font-size: xx-small;">Cantonese or Mandarin Speaking Market Research Surveyor</span></strong>&nbsp;<br /><span class="company">MIKADO Marketing</span>&nbsp;-&nbsp;<span class="location">Los Angeles, CA</span></div>\n<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class="snip">\n<p><strong>Company:&nbsp;</strong><br />We are a full service multicultural marketing agency based out of Colorado representing a vast number of clients who target the Chinese consumer in the US. We are looking to extend our network for local grassroots marketing activities within the local Chinese communities. Key areas include: Dallas, Houston, Los Angeles, San Francisco Bay Area, Seattle, Detroit, Chicago, Atlanta, Philadelphia/Pittsburg, D.C-VA- MD Metro, New Jersey and New York, Las Vegas, Miami, Boston, Denver.</p>\n<p><strong>Job Description:&nbsp;</strong><br />As a Market Research Surveyor you would work on a project basis. Projects include but aren&rsquo;t limited to; in person street intercepts (face to face surveys), in-store demos, event staffing and management, focus group coordination &amp; recruitment and other promotional activities as needed. Projects typically are held during the weekends.</p>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements:&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Must be bilingual:</li>\n<li>Fluent in English and Cantonese/Chinese</li>\n<li>Must have basic computer and Internet abilities along with own computer and the ability to use a tablet</li>\n<li>Be outgoing and personable</li>\n<li>Have keen market insight into the local ethnic communities, ethnic associations as well as an understanding of buying and media consumption habits of the targeted ethnicity.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Experience Required:&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Preferred 1-2 years experience in outside marketing, sales or promotional advertising/marketing</li>\n<li>Some college preferred/ HS Diploma required</li>\n<li>Experience conducting street intercepts is a plus</li>\n<li>Having a network of ethnic contacts is also a plus</li>\n<li>Ability to work in the U.S</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Compensation:&nbsp;</strong>$10 -$13 per survey (based on experience) and $15 per hour for events.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>', 'http://www.indeed.com/cmp/MIKADO-Marketing/jobs/Cantonese-or-Mandarin-Speaking-Market-Research-Surveyor-e418417afd1f43c4', '', 980, 104, 2),
(819, 1416367720, '珠宝顾问', 'Zales', 'Marketing', 'San Francisco, CA, United States', 'United States', 'California', 'San Francisco', 37.774929, -122.419418, '美国', '加利福尼亚州', '旧金山', 'None', 'Full Time', '<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class="snip">\n<p>Jewelry Consultant - Zales - Livermore Premium Outlets.<br />New Store, Opening 11/2014, Tier 1 Location</p>\n<p>At Zale, selling fine jewelry is our business, so it stands to reason that our store operations employees are the backbone of our business. These important positions are vital to the continuing success of our company. So, if you are enthusiastic about a dynamic working environment that focuses on people and their achievements, you will want to check out the employment opportunities at Zale- where you''ll have the chance to pursue a career, not just a job!</p>\n<p>Jewelry Consultants are responsible for identifying and fulfilling our guests'' jewelry needs, as well as maximizing personal and store performance. Jewelry Consultants learn from the best by undergoing a comprehensive new employee training program that teaches all the facets of selling fine jewelry - from making successful sales presentations, learning features and benefits of various types of merchandise, to building lifetime relationships with guests.</p>\n<p>Job Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fluently speak and understand Chinese (Mandarin / Cantonese).</li>\n<li>Results-oriented, strong communication skills, excellent customer service skills, a consistent work ethic and willingness to learn</li>\n<li>Must be able to multi-task and work in a team-friendly environment</li>\n<li>Prior retail, sales or customer service experience is preferred, but not required.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Compensation<br />Full time - $11 to $16 an hour. Large commission possibilities. Full tuition reimbursement*. Full Benefits. 401k. Vacation Pay. Sick Pay. Full job training. DCA Certification*. Employee Discounts.</p>\n<p>Part time - $11 to $15 an hour. Large commission possibilities. Partial Tuition Reimbursement. Full job training, Employee Discounts. Flexible Schedule.</p>\n<p>Successful Consultant will earn $45k to $80k a year, after commission.<br />Apply now</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>', 'http://www.indeed.com/cmp/Zales/jobs/Chinese-Language-Jewelry-Consultant-f2be98a4ae247e1a', '', 980, 106, 2),
(820, 1416422029, '【客户助理】【客户助理】【客户助理】招聘', '旅游服务咨询', 'Service', '美国纽约州纽约', 'United States', 'New York', 'New York', 40.712784, -74.005943, '美国', '纽约', '纽约', 'None', 'Full Time', '<p>我们是一家服务咨询公司，主要客户为来美高端华人客户，为其提供在美的生活商务活动等安排与接待。<br />现需招聘客户助理若干名<br />职位要求：<br />1.五官端正，气质佳，待人有亲和力，男女不限；<br />2.吃苦耐劳，学习能力强，愿意尝试服务行业；<br />3.无需经验，旅游或商务专业优先，中文交流流利，英文至少需要基本交流<br />以上为工作基本要求，如果对此职位感兴趣可以将简历发至我们邮箱，以便后续联系。</p>\n<p>E-mail：vincentxp@yeah.net<br />E-mail：vincentxp@yeah.net</p>', '', 'vincentxp@yeah.net', 1407, 150, 2),
