(842, 1416887260, 'Full-Time Passenger Sales ', 'EVA Airways', 'Marketing', 'Los Angeles, CA, United States', 'United States', 'California', 'Los Angeles', 34.052235, -118.243683, '美利坚合众国', 'California', 'Los Angeles', 'None', 'Full Time', '<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class="snip">\n<p><strong>ABOUT EVA AIRWAYS</strong></p>\n<p>EVA Airways (www.evaair.com) is an international airline headquartered in Taipei, Taiwan. Currently, Los Angeles Office has immediate entry-level openings for Passenger sales. Essential duties and responsibilities are listed below. Other duties may be assigned to meet business needs as required. EVA Airways offers an excellent benefits package, including comprehensive medical and dental insurance without premium costs, 401(k) plan with company match, free and discount flight tickets, etc. Please specify position and salary expectation on resume.</p>\n<p><strong>JOB DESCRIPTION</strong><br /><strong>FULL-TIME PASSENGER SALES:&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Establishes, develops and maintains business relationships with current customers and prospective customers in the assigned territory/market segment to generate new business for the organization&rsquo;s products/services</li>\n<li>Makes telephone calls and in-person visits and presentations to existing and prospective customers</li>\n<li>Researches sources for developing prospective customers and for information to determine their potential</li>\n<li>Expedites the resolution of customer problems and complaints</li>\n<li>Coordinates sales effort with marketing and management</li>\n<li>Analyzes the territory/market&rsquo;s potential and determines the value of existing and prospective customers&rsquo; value to the organization</li>\n<li>Identifies advantages and compares organization&rsquo;s products/services</li>\n<li>Plans and organizes personal sales strategy</li>\n<li>Supplies management with oral and written reports on customer needs, problems, interests, competitive activities, and potential for new businesses</li>\n<li>Participates in trade shows and conventions</li>\n<li>Some travels required</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>REQUIREMENTS:&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Bilingual English/Chinese a plus</li>\n<li>Good communication &amp; customer services skills</li>\n<li>Computer proficiency</li>\n<li>Self-motivated</li>\n</ul>\n<p><em>EVA Airways is an Equal Opportunity Employer.</em></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>', 'http://www.indeed.com/cmp/EVA-Airways/jobs/Full-Time-Passenger-Sales-480bc6b6529ac988', '', 980, 103, 2),
