(857, 1416969758, 'Contract Bilingual Interpreters (Chinese: Cantonese and Mandarin) 合同双语口译员（普通话/粤语）', 'Carmazzi Global Solutions', 'Language', 'Los Angeles, CA, United States', 'United States', 'California', 'Los Angeles', 34.052235, -118.243683, '美利坚合众国', 'California', 'Los Angeles', 'None', 'Part Time', '<p>DO NOT CALL OR EMAIL US, PLEASE COMPLETE THE APPLICATION USING THE LINK PROVIDED</p>\n<p>Carmazzi Global Solutions is seeking fluent, bilingual interpreters as Independent Contractors for On-Site Interpretation in Los Angeles, California.</p>\n<p>This is an on-call opportunity with flexible hours, and opportunity to develop skill. This is currently not a staff position and may be ideal for potential linguists who currently have a part time job that leaves some availability during normal business hours. Employment opportunities may arise in the future based on client need and individual performance.</p>\n<p>Primary Language Need: CHINESE (CANTONESE), CHINESE (MANDARIN)</p>\n<p>Professional experience as an interpreter is preferred but not required. Ideal experience includes community interpreting in the social service sector. Must be punctual, responsible, and have a reliable means of transportation.</p>\n<p>All interpreters will be required to complete a background check, credit check, and fingerprinting.<br />Salary of around $23 per hour based on experience and language pairs.</p>\n<p>Please use the link below to complete our linguist application so we may proceed in working with you.</p>\n<p>http://carmazzi.com/ssainterpreterapplication</p>\n<p>DO NOT CALL OR EMAIL US, PLEASE COMPLETE THE APPLICATION USING THE LINK PROVIDED</p>\n<p>With a network of more than 5,000 qualified linguists positioned around the world, Carmazzi Global Solutions excels in the full spectrum of language services, including localization, document translation, face-to-face and telephonic interpretation, and all aspects of globalization and multi-lingual marketing. Our mission is to enable worldwide clients to connect cultures&mdash;moving them from language to understanding and propelling them into an international presence with success in the global marketplace.</p>\n<p>Salary: $23.00 /hour</p>', 'http://www.indeed.com/cmp/Carmazzi-Global-Solutions/jobs/Contract-Bilingual-Interpreter-a6e5370e7d22a94c', '', 980, 168, 2),
(858, 1417045393, '本田汽车服务顾问', 'Diamond Honda of Puente Hills', 'Service', 'Industry, CA, United States', 'United States', 'California', 'City of Industry', 34.019733, -117.958672, '美利坚合众国', 'California', 'City of Industry', 'None', 'Full Time', '<div class="displayFieldBlock">\n<div class="displayField"><br /><strong>Automotive Service Advisor Fluent in Chinese - Diamond Honda of Puente Hills</strong><br />汽車服務顧問能說流利的中國 - 蓬特山鑽石本田<br /><br />If you believe Customer Service &nbsp;is a true craft -- one built on charisma, communication and thorough product knowledge - we want to talk to you!<br /><br />As a Service Advisor at Diamond Honda of Puente Hills you will be responsible to meet and greet service customers promptly in a professional and courteous manner.<br />Inspect vehicle and refer to service history to accurately identify and verify customer&rsquo;s service needs.<br />Promote the sales of appropriate services, parts, and accessories by thoroughly understanding the product and associated service requirements.&nbsp;<br />Provide accurate cost and time of completion estimates for the services recommended, communicate and get proper authorization from customers.<br />Check on progress of services to vehicles throughout the day and contact customer to communicate and receive approval regarding any changes in the cost-estimate, promised time of delivery or recommended services.<br />Administer new and used vehicle warranty repairs in accordance with manufacturer warranty guidelines.<br />Confirm service appointments by telephone the day before the customer is scheduled to arrive and conduct post-repair follow up.<br />Inspect vehicles prior to each customer delivery to ensure vehicles services and/or repairs are performed correctly and communicate the results with the customer.<br />Meet requirements of the state and federal law for automobile repair and consumer protection.<br />Demonstrates behaviors consistent with the Company&rsquo;s Values in all interactions with customers, co-workers and vendors.<br /><br />如果您认为客户服务是一个真正的手艺 - 一个建立在人格魅力，沟通和深入的产品知识 - 我们想和你谈谈！&nbsp;<br /><br />作为一名服务顾问在蓬特山钻石本田，你将负责满足并以专业，礼貌和及时的服务迎接客户。&nbsp;<br />检查车辆并参照服务历史，准确地识别和确认客户的服务需求。&nbsp;<br />通过深入了解产品和相关服务的要求促进适当的服务，零部件和配件的销售。&nbsp;<br />为完成预算的服务推荐准确的成本和时间，沟通，从客户获得适当授权。&nbsp;<br />检查车辆服务的进步整个白天和接触客户进行沟通，并接收有关的成本估计变更的批准，承诺的交货或推荐的服务时间。&nbsp;<br />按照制造商的保修管理指引新的和二手车保修期内的维修。&nbsp;<br />通过电话确认预约服务，当天客户预定到达并进行维修后跟进之前。&nbsp;<br />之前，每个客户交付的车辆进行检查，以保证车辆的服务和/或维修正确执行和沟通的结果与客户。&nbsp;<br />符合州和联邦法律对汽车修理和消费者保护的要求。&nbsp;<br />演示与本公司与客户，同事和供应商的所有交互价值观一致的行为。</div>\n</div>\n<div class="displayFieldBlock">\n<h3>Job Requirements:</h3>\n<div class="displayField"><br />Two or more years of previous experience as a service advisor.<br />High school diploma or equivalent.<br />Valid driver license in the state that you will work and a good driving record.<br />Great attitude with high-energy personality.<br />Excellent customer service skills.<br />Professional appearance and work ethic.<br />Ability to work well in a process driven environment.<br />Outstanding communication skills in both verbal and written.<br /><br />Benefits at Diamond Honda of Puente Hills include a lucrative compensation plan, paid time off, medical, dental, 401(k), life, and disability insurance, and employee vehicle purchase program.<br /><br />两年或两年以上的经验作为服务顾问。&nbsp;<br />高中毕业文凭或同等学历。&nbsp;<br />有效的驾驶执照，你将工作状态和良好的驾驶记录。&nbsp;<br />伟大的态度与高能量的个性。&nbsp;<br />优秀的客户服务技巧。&nbsp;<br />专业的外观和职业道德。&nbsp;<br />能够在一个流程驱动的环境中很好地工作。&nbsp;<br />出色的沟通技巧，口头和书面。&nbsp;<br /><br />在蓬特山钻石本田好处包括一个利润丰厚的补偿计划，带薪休假，医疗，牙科，401（K），生命和残疾保险，员工和车辆购置计划。<br /><br />&nbsp;\n<p><strong>Its time to make the most important move of your career!</strong><br /><br /><strong>Apply now!</strong></p>\n<br /><strong>We would really like to hear from you!</strong><br /><br />Please contact<br /><br /><strong>Jon Martin</strong><br /><br />Service Director<br /><br /><br /></div>\n</div>', '', 'jmartin@diamondhonda.com', 980, 128, 2),
(859, 1417045676, '会计助理/行政助理', 'Winjet Automotive Inc', 'Finance', 'Industry, CA, United States', 'United States', 'California', 'City of Industry', 34.019733, -117.958672, '美利坚合众国', 'California', 'City of Industry', 'None', 'Full Time', '<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class="snip">\n<p>We are a fast growing manufacture company in Auto Parts Industry located in City of Industry CA 91745, and seeking a Sales Representatives positions in FULL TIME to join our Team. You may find more information from our website: www.winjetinc.com</p>\n<p>Accounting Assistant/ Administrative Assistant</p>\n<ul>\n<li>2 years+ accounting experience</li>\n<li>Data entry, Filing, Familiar w/ Microsoft Office/ QuickBooks</li>\n<li>Self motivated, able to handle multi-tasks &amp; detail oriented</li>\n<li>College Degree; Bilingual in English/ Chinese</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:<br />1) Excellent written &amp; verbal comm skills<br />2) Must be bilingual in English and Chinese (if you are not fluent in BOTH languages please do not apply)<br />3) Legal working status</p>\n<p>================================================================<br />If you are interested in this position, please reply to this email with the questions below and let us know what date and time is the best to interview.</p>\n<p>Questions:<br />1) Are you H1 working status or permanent working status?<br />2) What was your salary before?<br />3) What is your expected salary?</p>\n<p>Send resume &amp; salary history expectations: amypoon(@)winjetinc.com</p>\n<p>================================================================</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Please do not apply if you are not fluent in BOTH languages</li>\n<li>No phone calls or walk ins will be accepted.</li>\n<li>EMAIL ONLY</li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>', 'http://www.indeed.com/cmp/Winjet-Automotive-Inc/jobs/Accounting-Assistant-Administrative-Assistant-e51665d377a78441', '', 980, 150, 2),
