 effective management, leadership, time management and organizational skills necessary&nbsp;<br />&bull; Knowledge of local, state and federal labor and employment laws&nbsp;<br />&bull; Effective presentation and facilitation skills required&nbsp;<br /><strong>We Offer an Outstanding Compensation and Benefits Package, Which Includes:&nbsp;<br />&bull;&nbsp;</strong>Medical and Dental Insurance&nbsp;<br />&bull; Free Life Insurance and Long Term Disability&nbsp;<br />&bull; Voluntary Vision Insurance&nbsp;<br />&bull; Supplemental Life Insurance&nbsp;<br />&bull; Cash Balance Retirement Plan&nbsp;<br />&bull; 401k plan with company match&nbsp;<br />&bull; Paid Vacation&nbsp;<br />&bull; Paid Absence Plan&nbsp;<br />&bull; Tuition Reimbursement Program</p>', 'http://www.indeed.com/viewjob?jk=e4f7655abb9f4b16&q=chinese&l=Los+Angeles%2C+CA&tk=19an7ol2d1d4i2j3', '', 980, 210, 2),
