(911, 1418606990, '搜索引擎优化地区经理/中国', 'VoyagerMed', 'Technology', 'New York, NY, United States', 'United States', 'New York', 'New York', 40.712784, -74.005943, '美国', 'New York', 'New York', 'None', 'Full Time', '<p>Are you passionate in Search Engine Optimization? Do you enjoy working in an international environment? Then come and join our team and become part of our further success!</p>\n<p>VoyagerMed is the premier &ldquo;destination healthcare&rdquo; company that enables doctors and patients to access cutting edge medical technology anywhere in the world at an affordable price. As a global healthcare platform, VOYAGERMED brings together internationally accredited hospitals and an experienced customer service team. Whether you are looking for a reasonably priced knee replacement or a plastic surgery performed as soon as possible, VOYAGERMED is where patients and doctors connect.</p>\n<p>Your Tasks:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>You will write long and interesting articles about medical treatments</li>\n<li>You will prepare press releases and contact journalists</li>\n<li>You will help to translate and check the quality of our website</li>\n<li>You will do on-page/off-page search engine optimization</li>\n<li>You will regularly contact webmasters over the phone and emails in order to establish business partnerships</li>\n<li>You will analyze the results of the performance</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Your Profile:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>You are interested in Online Marketing and highly motivated to learn something new</li>\n<li>You are creative and have excellent writing skills</li>\n<li>You speak English on a native level and a plus is to have good communication skills in Chinese.</li>\n<li>You are open and honest and feel very comfortable communicating over the phone and email</li>\n<li>You enjoy working in a young environment with exciting challenges and tasks</li>\n<li>You have some basic knowledge of Excel</li>\n<li>Knowledge of technical SEO is a plus</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Our offer</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Join a fun, international and highly-motivated team of outstanding talents in a supportive environment with a high performance culture</li>\n<li>The opportunity to be responsible for and manage your own projects</li>\n<li>Access to a well-established network in New York&rsquo;s start-up scene</li>\n<li>Work directly with decision makers and have an impact in the organization</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Excited by the prospect of joining us? If so, we look forward to receiving your application. Send us an email with your resume and short motivation letter outlining your availability and the type of internship you want to do to.</p>\n<p>Please understand that we cannot accept applications from graduates, or any applications that do not specify the type of internship you are applying for.</p>\n<p>Please include into the subject line &ldquo;SEO Country Manager / China&rdquo;.</p>\n<p>If you have any questions, please do not hesitate to contact us via email. We look forward to hearing from you! For further information you may visit our website at www.VoyagerMed.com.</p>', 'http://www.indeed.com/cmp/VoyagerMed/jobs/SEO-Country-Manager-e0d12a44e428bc55', '', 980, 140, 2),
