(1004, 1422680158, 'Functional QA Intern', 'KANA', 'Technology', 'Santa Clara, CA, United States', 'United States', 'California', 'Santa Clara', 37.354107, -121.955238, '美国', 'California', 'Santa Clara', 'None', 'Internship', '<table border="0" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="2">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td colspan="2" width="100%">\n<p><strong>【实习机会/Santa Clara, CA】KANA提供Functional QA Intern机会. 要求: 精通Java Programming; 了解quality assurance methodology; Preferred - 了解functional testing tool (Selenium a plus), 沟通能力, 了解relational databases (Oracle, DB2, SQL2005).Overview of Job Function</strong></p>\n<p>We are looking for an exceptional individual to join our Engineering team as a Software Quality Assurance Intern. The Q/A Intern assist with the development of our enterprise software products by working with a team of software developers and Q/A peers. This is an excellent opportunity for a student looking to get his or her feet wet in the software development industry.</p>\n<p><strong>Principal Duties and Essential Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Performing testing tasks such as planning, scheduling and testing software products to ensure products meet design specifications and functionality requirements;</li>\n<li>Verifying through product testing that product meets total quality management limits and standards; and</li>\n<li>Assisting product developers and technical support specialists in resolving product defects.</li>\n<li>Execute automation to test enterprise software and work on in-house automation</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Minimum Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>A good understanding of quality assurance methodology;</li>\n<li>Proficiency in Java Programming</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Preferred Requirement</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Knowledge of any functional testing tool &ndash; Selenium is a plus</li>\n<li>Knowledge of various operating systems;</li>\n<li>Working knowledge of relational databases - Oracle, DB2 and SQL2005;</li>\n<li>Excellent analytical and problem-solving skills;</li>\n<li>Excellent organizational skills and attention to detail;</li>\n<li>Excellent verbal and written communication skills; and</li>\n<li>The willingness to learn and grow in a challenging environment.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;ADDITIONAL INFORMATION</p>\n<p>&nbsp;<strong>Office Location:&nbsp;</strong>KANA''s US headquarters is located in&nbsp;<strong>Santa Clara, CA&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;<strong>Duration:&nbsp;</strong>This is a Internship position.</p>\n<p><em>KANA is an Equal Opportunity Employer and we welcome candidates from diverse backgrounds.</em></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan="2" width="100%">\n<p>As an equal opportunity employer, Verint Systems Inc. prides itself in providing employees with a work environment in which all individuals are treated with respect and dignity. This means we are committed to providing equal opportunity to all qualified employees and applicants for employment without regard to one&rsquo;s race, color, religion, national origin, age, gender, disability, alienage or citizenship status, marital status, creed, genetic predisposition or carrier status, sexual orientation, Veteran status or any other classification protected by applicable federal, state or local laws. This policy applies to all terms and conditions of employment including but not limited to hiring, placement, promotion, compensation, training, leave of absence or termination.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>', 'http://ch.tbe.taleo.net/CH02/ats/careers/requisition.jsp?org=VERINT&cws=63&rid=9480&source=Indeed.com', '', 980, 479, 2),
