(1070, 1426148316, '合伙人，国际市场营销总监 | Partner, Global Marketing Director', 'Drderma Inc.', 'Marketing', 'San Francisco, CA, United States', 'United States', 'California', 'San Francisco', 37.774929, -122.419418, '美国', 'California', 'San Francisco', 'None', 'Full Time', '<ol>\n<li><strong style="font-size: 11px;">要什么的人</strong><strong style="font-size: 11px;">?</strong></li>\n</ol>\n<p>职务：合伙人，国际市场营销总监</p>\n<p>我们要的不仅是合伙人，更是灵魂伴侣。</p>\n<p>要有独立创新精神，要与众不同，要敢于挑战大公司。</p>\n<p>有TMT、移动医疗经验者优先。</p>\n<p>工作地点：硅谷</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ol start="2">\n<li><strong>为什么要这样的人?</strong></li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>我</strong><strong>们</strong><strong>立志成</strong><strong>为</strong><strong>皮肤美容界的</strong><strong>Amazon</strong><strong>。</strong></p>\n<p>我们拥有良好的发展前景和雄厚的技术实力。</p>\n<p>我们决定从硅谷走向全球。</p>\n<p>我们缺国际化的市场营销合伙人。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ol start="3">\n<li><strong>怎么</strong><strong>干？</strong></li>\n</ol>\n<p>1)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 作为我们硅谷公司的核心人物，领导开发品牌属性；</p>\n<p>2)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 利用移动互联网发起Kindle模式的市场营销；</p>\n<p>3)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 组建全球营销体系，主要是线上市场推广；</p>\n<p>4)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 协助团队通过FDA、CE、ISO认证;</p>\n<p>5)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 建立北美及欧洲的核心示范展示点；</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ol start="4">\n<li><strong>具体要求：</strong></li>\n</ol>\n<p>(1)&nbsp; 有TMT行业、移动医疗行业工作经验优先；</p>\n<p>(2)&nbsp; 年龄30 &mdash; 42岁；</p>\n<p>(3)&nbsp; 擅长打造团队，有强烈的创业精神；</p>\n<p>(4)&nbsp; 我们只要最顶级的市场营销总监；</p>\n<p>(5)&nbsp; 必须要有丰富的国际化经验；</p>\n<p>(6)&nbsp; 会中文者优先。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ol start="5">\n<li><strong>我</strong><strong>们</strong><strong>提供的待遇：</strong></li>\n</ol>\n<p>1)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 不拘一格的创新环境和一群有才华、有意思的团队；</p>\n<p>2)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 分红和股权；</p>\n<p>3)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 公司有三年内IPO计划。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ol start="6">\n<li><strong>公司背景？</strong></li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 我们是一家崇尚产品至上的中国顶尖激光公司，旗下具有家用产品事业部，医疗产品事业部，以及生活美容产品事业部。产品涉及激光、射频、超声等技术领域，提供皮肤病治疗、皮肤年轻化、生发等产品，拥有强大的高尖端研发团队。公司效益良好，正处于 IPO阶段。</p>\n<p><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;请符合条件的并有意加入我们的大牛们，将简历通过平台提交，或者私信于我：<a href="mailto:vivianwang2015@outlook.com">vivianwang2015@outlook.com</a>。对于符合条件的候选人，我们会以最快的速度与您联系，届时我们会坦诚且详细的回答您所有的问题。 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<p>--- &nbsp;来自于疯狂的颠覆的团队&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>1. What we want?</strong></p>\n<p>Job title: Partner, Global Marketing Director</p>\n<p>What we want is not only a business partner, but also a soul partner.</p>\n<p>You are independent and creative.</p>\n<p>You think different.</p>\n<p>You dare to challenge the large companies.</p>\n<p>Location: Silicon Valley, CA, U.S.A.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>2. Why we want?</strong></p>\n<p>We aspire to be another Amazon in Skin Care Industry.</p>\n<p>We have bright future and strong technical strength.</p>\n<p>We decide to go to the world from Silicon Valley.</p>\n<p>We need global marketing partner.</p>\n<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<p><strong>3. How to do it?</strong></p>\n<p>1)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; As a core role of our Silicon Valley company, leading to develop our brand attributes;</p>\n<p>2)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Use mobile internet to launch &lsquo;Kindle&rsquo; marketing mode;</p>\n<p>3)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Build up global marketing system, especially E-marketing;</p>\n<p>4)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Support our team to get FDA, CE, and ISO certificates;</p>\n<p>5)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Set up core center in North America and Europe.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>4. Desired Skills and Experience?</strong></p>\n<p>1)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; TMT and Mobile Medical industry work experience is preferred;&nbsp;</p>\n<p>2)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Age between 30 - 40 years;</p>\n<p>3)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Specialize in creating team, having a strong entrepreneurial spirit;</p>\n<p>4)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; We only want the best marketing director;</p>\n<p>5)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Has wealthy international experience;</p>\n<p>6)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Good spoken and written Chinese and English to fulfill daily work communications.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>5. </strong><strong>We provide:</strong></p>\n<p>1)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Flexible innovation environment + Talented and interesting team;</p>\n<p>2)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Dividends and share;</p>\n<p>3)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; IPO plans within three years;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>6. Company background?</strong></p>\n<p>We are a Chinese leading laser company, advocating &ldquo;the product supreme&rdquo;, which has home products division, medical products division, and life cosmetology products division. Our products focus on laser, radio frequency, and ultrasound technology, etc., including but not limited to skin treatment, skin care, and hair growth. We have an extremely strong experienced and qualified Research &amp; Development team. The business operation status our company is quite good, and we are in the stage of IPO.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>If you are a good fit and interested in the opportunity, please submit your resume via the system or my personal email: <a href="mailto:vivianwang2015@outlook.com">vivianwang2015@outlook.com</a>. For qualified candidate, we will contact you ASAP, and answer any of your questions with all our sincerity.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>--- From a crazy and subversive team</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>___</p>\n<p>只有那些疯狂到自认为可以改变世界的人，最终改变了我们的世界。</p>\n<p>The people who are crazy enough to think they can change the world are the ones who do.</p>\n<p>你，准备好了吗?</p>', '', 'vivianwang2015@outlook.com', 1754, 204, 2),
(1073, 1426050131, '纽约MIDTOWN公司诚请外勤员工：', 'MIDTOWN', 'Consulting', '美国纽约州纽约', 'United States', 'New York', 'New York', 40.712784, -74.005943, '美国', 'New York', 'New York', 'None', 'Full Time', '<p>工作性质：需要半天出外勤到政府机构办事，半天在办公室处理文档，接听电话。</p>\n<p>要求：有合法工作身份，性格耐心工作细心，能基本中英文沟通。基本电脑软件操做，愿意虚心学习。一周五天，9-5. <br /> <br /> 待遇：最低时薪起, 不扣除午餐时间，有交通补助。<br /> 工作地点：曼哈顿中城。</p>\n<p>工作不累，适合需要长期稳定工作的人士申请，请把基本情况或简历发到forbusinessticket@gmail.com</p>', '', 'forbusinessticket@gmail.com', 1761, 2, 2),
