(1072, 1425963777, '现诚招三名业务代表', '纽约信用卡服务公司(payment processing)', 'Finance', '美国纽约州纽约', 'United States', 'New York', 'New York', 40.712784, -74.005943, '美国', 'New York', 'New York', 'None', 'Full Time', '<p>纽约信用卡服务公司(payment processing)欲扩大美国市场，现诚招三名业务代表。业务代表将在华尔街总公司完成一个月的试用期与培训，表现良好者可留下全职。</p>\n<p>要求中英文流利（会粤语闽南语福州话上海话等方言更好）。擅长与人交流。</p>\n<p>（可转正，办h1b,支持OPT,CPT挂靠）</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>具体要求如下</p>\n<p>Qualifications:</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Bilingual in Chinese and English is required;(良好的英语中文技能)</li>\n<li>Self-motivated with positive attitude;（积极向上的态度）</li>\n<li>Ability to work independently without constant supervision;（自觉工作的的能力）</li>\n<li>Good Communication Skills;（良好的沟通技能）</li>\n<li>Previous cold-calling/face-to-face sales experience a PLUS;（有电话销售经验者优先）</li>\n<li>Previous experience in the Merchant Service industry a PLUS;（有相关工作经验者优先）</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Responsibilities（职责）:</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Prospect and pitch leads through a soft sell approach while building and</li>\n</ul>\n<p>maintaining relationships;（在建立维持关系的同时有良好的前景预判与渐进销售）</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Build quality sales relationships with both new clients and existing</li>\n</ul>\n<p>clients;（与新老客户建立良好的关系）</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Build and maintaining relationships with affiliate offices（建立新的子公司）;</li>\n<li>Be responsive to client&rsquo;s needs and work to foster the growth of our</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Business over time（重视客户需求建立长久良好的关系）;</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Create and maintain marketing programs to increase sales（建立维持长久的市场计划）.</li>\n<li>Clients management and customer support（客户维护与支持）</li>\n</ul>\n<p>. Ability to travel 50% of the time （一半以上的出差时间）</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>公司地址：wall st &amp; williams st, New York</p>\n<p>工作地点：in Wall st for first month, then Chicago area</p>\n<p>工作时间：full time: 10am to 6pm, monday-friday/ part time</p>\n<p>薪酬：performance based salary, with bonus</p>\n<p>有意者请投简历至wade@argusinvision.com</p>', '', 'wade@argusinvision.com', 980, 345, 2),
