(1098, 1427072445, '招聘金融投资合作伙伴', '地点不限', 'Finance', 'New York, NY, United States', 'United States', 'New York', 'New York', 40.712784, -74.005943, '美国', 'New York', 'New York', 'None', 'Internship', '<p>为什么别人会赚钱？<br />这是许多人苦苦思考的问题：其实会赚钱的人并不一定比别人聪明丶能干，而关健在于会抓住机会丶会借力；<br />为什么华尔街的人会赚大钱？关键在于会用钱生钱，会投资技巧！<br />为什么许多人仍在找机会丶出苦力丶看老板的脸色丶朝九晚五的工作？</p>\n<p>下面给您一些机会，看你能否抓住：<br />本人经过多年的苦心研究，在美股研究方面有一套可靠稳定的办法。<br />1, 免费尝试美股交易. 1--2个月;<br />2，现招聘金融投资合作伙伴：你若有资金 . 你开户，我操盘，待1-2个月你满意后再扩大合作资金；或你介绍朋友，待成功后，按利润给你提成。<br />如有诚意，请发邮件联系：blackhorseny@gmail.com</p>', '', 'blackhorseny@gmail.com', 1745, 2, 2),
(1099, 1427083138, '兼职音乐老师', 'Avenues: The World School', 'Management', 'Los Angeles, CA, United States', 'United States', 'California', 'Los Angeles', 34.052235, -118.243683, '美国', 'California', 'Los Angeles', 'None', 'Part Time', '<div class="description-module container">\n<div class="content">\n<div class="description-section">\n<h3 class="sub-header">Job description</h3>\n<div class="rich-text">Avenues: The World School is looking for a part-time Mandarin Chinese speaking music teacher in our Lower School division (kindergarten to fourth grade). Avenues runs a language immersion program in the Lower School, and the students receive their music instruction in Mandarin Chinese and Spanish. The part time position is two days per week. The school is flexible as to which two days of the week.<br /><br />Music, theater, dance and movement are an intrinsic part of younger children&rsquo;s day at Avenues. Younger students will participate in an age-appropriate progression of music instruction that includes singing, rhythmic movement, and making music with Orff instruments. As students grow older, music instruction will be a fundamental part of the Lower School curriculum. Students will continue to build on their knowledge and understanding of the components of music in song and on instruments.<br /><br />The music teacher should be creative in the use of age-appropriate technologies, expert in communication with parents of children of these ages and excited to work with young children and their parents. Candidates must have training and teaching experience in Dalcroze, Kod&aacute;ly and Orff-Schulwerk approaches. Keyboard skill is strongly preferable.<br /><br />Candidates should have at least three years of music instruction and ideally exposure to immersion education. Collaboration and valuing the importance of inter-disciplinary work are important qualities of our teachers. Candidates should also possess a B.A. or B.S. and commensurate teaching experience of childre