(1125, 1427935898, '招聘金融投资合作伙伴', 'ABC', 'Finance', 'New York, NY, United States', 'United States', 'New York', 'New York', 40.712784, -74.005943, '美国', 'New York', 'New York', 'None', 'Part Time', '<p><strong>为什么别人会赚钱？ 这是许多人苦苦思考的问题：其实会赚钱的人并不一定比别人聪明丶能干，而关健在于会抓住机会丶会借力； 为什么华尔街的人会赚大钱？关键在于会用钱生钱，会投资技巧！ 为什么许多人仍在找机会丶出苦力丶看老板的脸色丶朝九晚五的工作？</strong></p>\n<p><strong>下面给您一些机会，看你能否抓住： 本人经过多年的苦心研究，在美股研究方面有一套可靠稳定的办法。 1, 免费尝试美股交易. 1--2个月; 2，现招聘金融投资合作伙伴：你若有资金 . 你开户，我操盘，待1-2个月你满意后再扩大合作资金；或你介绍朋友，待成功后，按利润给你提成。 如有诚意，请发邮件联系：blackhorseny@gmail.com</strong></p>', '', '', 1745, 3, 0),
(1126, 1427980465, 'Manager assitant/ Trainee Manager 经理助理／储备干部', 'leopard inc', 'Management', 'Hillside, NJ, United States', 'United States', 'New Jersey', 'Hillside', 40.695503, -74.228729, '美国', 'New Jersey', 'Hillside', 'H1B', 'Full Time', '<p>Leopard Inc., Building on more than 15 years of experience, Leopard Tire is dedicated to providing the commercial / passenger tire industry the best technology, service and value available.<br />Leopard Inc. is seeking manager assistant to promote wholesale truck tires and tire handling work at our franchise company at Charleston, South Carolina.&nbsp;<strong>May need be trained 2 weeks at Hillside, New Jersey&nbsp;</strong><br /><strong>Duties include but are not limited to the following:</strong><br />- Managing current customer accounts.<br />- Managing deliveries and inventory.<br />- Developing and maintaining a thorough knowledge of products and services to provide accurate information to customers.&nbsp;<br />- Ensuring prompt resolution of tire adjustments and ensuring that customer casings are handled appropriately. Delivering tires to customers as needed.<br />- Maintaining company property in accordance with company policy.<br />- Assisting with a variety of duties within the assigned location, such as attending to customers, maintaining inventory, moving and stacking tires, and other duties as required.<br /><br />REQUIREMENTS:<br />- Must be willing to follow all safety procedures and work in a safe manner.<br />- Must be able to work in a results-oriented, fast-paced environment as part of a team.<br />-Must have a valid driver license, Class A is major plus.&nbsp;<br />- Good oral and written communication ability.<br />-bilingual (Mandarin, Cantonese or Spanish) is plus.<br />We do anticipate providing sponsorship for employment h1-b visa for this employment position.</p>\n<p>-公司更倾向于能文能武的男士</p>\n<p>Emails without resume will not response.&nbsp;<br />Contact: Kevin. Email: kevin@truck-tire.com</p>', '', 'kevin@truck-tire.com', 823, 190, 1),
(1128, 1428071189, '招聘兼职/全职/Intern 銷售员', 'ULMS', 'Marketing', 'Fremont, CA, United States', 'United States', 'California', 'Fremont', 37.548271, -121.988571, '美国', 'California', 'Fremont', 'None', 'Part Time', '<p>（略懂英文也可）, 可致电(408) 329-1180 询问详情, 工作时间灵活</p>\n<p><br /><span style="font-size: large;">Our company is located in fremont and we are forming a new sales team.</span><span style="font-size: large;"><br /></span><span style="font-size: large;"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Title: Sales Consultant</span></span><br /><br />Job description:&nbsp;<br />*Generating calls and prospecting potential clients<br />*Conducting calling and in-person meeting with clients&nbsp;<br />*Building and maintaining relationships with affilates<br /><br />Qualification:<br />*Strong desire to succeed<br />*Be able to work independently and driven by results<br />*Previous phone/face-to-face sales experience is a PLUS but not required<br />*Bilingual skills is a PLUS but not required<br /><br />Compensation:<br />*Base payment with minimum quota requirement<br />*Commission &amp; Bonus<br />*Promotion opportunities *Network with experienced people<br /><br />If you are interested, feel free to contact by (408) 329-1180 and speak to our manager.</p>', '', 'apple2000ca@gmail.com', 1774, 102, 1),
(1129, 1428076533, '招聘销售业务精英', 'Menu Office', 'Technology', 'Rockville, MD, United States', 'United States', 'Maryland', 'Rockville', 39.083996, -77.152756, '美国', 'Maryland', 'Rockville', 'None', 'Full Time', '<p>Menu Office位于马里兰洲，主要服务领域是餐馆网络点餐系统，网页设计和广告设计营销。</p>\n<p>现诚招销售业务精英数名，要求如下：</p>\n<p>擅长营销、策划、销售，男女不限</p>\n<p>如表现优越，本公司可为有需要的员工代办身份</p>\n<p>底薪+提成<br />有意者请发送简历至：contact@menuoffice.com</p>', '', 'contact@menuoffice.com', 1833, 92, 1),
(1130, 1428088355, '招聘市场推广实习生', 'www.redcubestudio.com', 'Marketing', 'South San Francisco, CA, United States', 'United States', 'California', 'South San Francisco', 37.654655, -122.407753, '美国', 'California', 'South San Francisco', 'None', 'Internship', '<p>【实习机会/san francisco, CA】招聘市场推广实习生，三个月后可转正。 主要职责是负责本公司媒体宣传和推广，大学在校生可申请，要求对媒体宣传，视频推广有热情，办公地点：南旧金山。 有车的同学最佳。&nbsp;</p>\n<p>公司网站：www.redcubestudio.com</p>\n<p>邮箱：pingo@redcubestudio.com</p>\n<p>电话：718.552.6556</p>', '', 'pingo@redcubestudio.com', 1834, 123, 1),
